Create an 'extlib' subdirectory, then acquire and place the following
Jar files into that subdirectory-

apache-commons-lang.jar
tomcat-servlet-api.jar
commons-collections-3.2.jar
velocity.jar

Make sure Tomcat/lib includes the following jars:
 * apache-commons-dbcp.jar
 * apache-commons-pool.jar
 * mysql-connector-java.jar

Create a directory to store uploaded files, e.g. /srv/falcon-contest-files.

Create a Mysql database. Import schema.sql into then new database.

Modify the context.xml file with your database connection information,
and the path of the uploaded-files directory.

